  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">Related</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Other holding cabinet service.</h2>
    <ul class="bullet-list">
      <li><a href="/commercial/holding-cabinet-repair/">Holding cabinet repair (parent pillar)</a></li>
      <li><a href="/commercial/holding-cabinet-repair/temperature-fluctuating/">Temperature fluctuating</a> · <a href="/commercial/holding-cabinet-repair/door-seal-issues/">Door seal issues</a> · <a href="/commercial/holding-cabinet-repair/humidity-control-failure/">Humidity control failure</a></li>
      <li><a href="/commercial/holding-cabinet-repair/brands/alto-shaam/">Alto-Shaam</a> · <a href="/commercial/holding-cabinet-repair/brands/cres-cor/">Cres Cor</a> · <a href="/commercial/holding-cabinet-repair/brands/hatco/">Hatco</a> · <a href="/commercial/holding-cabinet-repair/brands/metro/">Metro</a> · <a href="/commercial/holding-cabinet-repair/brands/vollrath/">Vollrath</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bottom-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Holding cabinet not heating during service? Same-day priority.</h2>
    <p>Alto-Shaam, Cres Cor, Hatco, Metro, Vollrath across LA, OC, Ventura. $120 commercial diagnostic, waived with repair. BHGS #A49573, EPA 608 Universal #1346255700410.</p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href={phoneHref} class="btn-primary">☎ Call {phone}</a>
